{"tid":669104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國新垣結衣日本竄紅 , 拍日劇中國高人氣","createTime":"2018-05-18T08:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T07:22:29.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfc78b470c200756f18a669bd04751218a77cc6","tid":669104,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"「強國新垣結衣」演日劇　處女秀扮制服妹<br />\n<br />\n中國網紅龍夢柔因神似新垣結衣竄紅，得到客串日劇的機會<br />\n<br />\n22歲中國網紅龍夢柔，因神似新垣結衣紅到日本，日前拍了北海道限定旅遊廣告，這次觸角伸向日本全國，客串日劇《愛情重跑》（暫譯），今天深夜將播出。<br />\n <br />\n這也是她的戲劇處女秀，劇中飾演高中生IG網紅，並沿用她現實中的IG暱稱「栗子」。她表示：「作夢都沒想到自己會演日劇，而且我從以前就很喜歡日本的高中制服，這次很開心能穿上制服演出。」<br />\n <br />\n談到未來的目標，她笑說想參與《名偵探柯南》的動畫配音，如果有中國人的角色，她一定要挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"http://p3.ifengimg.com/a/2018_20/b93e8503c60d803_size42_w558_h368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.ifengimg.com%2Fa%2F2018_20%2Fb93e8503c60d803_size42_w558_h368.jpg&h=609e8ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180517/640_11718f144420aedc74b5d0c976710347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180517%2F640_11718f144420aedc74b5d0c976710347.jpg&h=46b43c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180517/640_2a9b1ee1d4e62ddb1047309754d153f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180517%2F640_2a9b1ee1d4e62ddb1047309754d153f3.jpg&h=9bda0d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img3.guangsuss.com/4d3c192273642f4c8a918b6ddc3a14cd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.guangsuss.com%2F4d3c192273642f4c8a918b6ddc3a14cd&h=47c23038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceb6cbf8f1345c2e273e3ef13c2e6d7b90113c16","tid":669104,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"整容？"},{"pid":"0da462b83b938310c157a49144816a0f0bed3283","tid":669104,"uid":93784,"l